Class: AuthenticationResult

AuthenticationResult

new AuthenticationResult(authenticationResult)

Encapsulates an authentication result, and provides a method for getting the account that was authenticated.

Parameters:
Name Type Description
authenticationResult Object

The JSON response from the Stormpath API, when making a POST request against an applications /loginAttempts endpoint.

Properties
Name Type Description
account.href Object

The HREF of the account that authenticated.
